"ヒー<br>ベジタリアン・ヴィーガン対応メニューもご用意しています"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Access the rates from the same menu to see how price rules apply during the "
